public interface MHealthAtlasAppRepository
extends org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaRepository<MHealthAtlasApp,​java.lang.Long>
Contains methods to interact with the database.
The query annotations uses the entity classes defined in MHealthAtlasApp. Standart actions like save and findAllById are automatically generated.
